name: 3d SOCIAL (Free icons pack)
description:
Hello, my name is Anatoly.

I designed this free pack of 3d social media icons.

You can use it absolutely free, but if you want to leave a thank you or make an offer, then write to me on telegram @a2_shr, I will be glad. I will also be glad to your likes in the community.

Thank you all in advance.


P.S. These 3d icons use effects and styles, so use the Scale (K) function to scale.
